#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:1
msgid "E4173"
msgstr "E4173"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `invalid_value_type_attr`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`invalid_value_type_attr`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:5
msgid "Invalid `#valtype` declaration."
msgstr "无效的 `#valtype` 声明。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:7
msgid ""
"`#valtype` asks the compiler to represent a type as a value type. Not "
"every type shape can be represented this way. The compiler rejects "
"declarations that would require boxed or runtime-object storage, such as "
"a type parameter field, an object field, a mutable field, too many "
"fields, or a nested value type field."
msgstr ""
"`#valtype` 要求编译器将某个类型表示为值类型。并不是所有类型形状都能这样表示。"
"如果声明需要装箱或运行时对象存储，编译器会拒绝它，例如包含类型参数字段、对象"
"字段、可变字段、过多字段或嵌套值类型字段。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:12
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:14
msgid ""
"#valtype\n"
"struct Box[T] {\n"
"  value : T\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:18
msgid ""
"The field `value` has type `T`, a type parameter. A value type must have "
"a concrete supported layout, so this generic field is rejected."
msgstr ""
"字段 `value` 的类型是类型参数 `T`。值类型必须具有具体且受支持的布局，因此这个"
"泛型字段会被拒绝。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:21
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:23
msgid ""
"Use concrete scalar fields for the value type, or remove `#valtype` if "
"the type needs a generic or boxed layout."
msgstr ""
"为值类型使用具体的标量字段；如果该类型需要泛型布局或装箱布局，则移除 "
"`#valtype`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4173.md:26
msgid ""
"#valtype\n"
"struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"  y : Int\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

